author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
"Building 650" is by Squid and I didn't know what to expect. Having listened to it,  now I don't know what to think, but I enjoyed it. I think. Squid's new album "Cowards" comes out next month. 

To listen to the song and to watch the video for "Building 650" uninterrupted, you can find it here: https://youtu.be/oFlgMauJO9o?si=Zd1ScVniX_04PjkC

The new Darkness album comes out in March, you can pre-order 'Dreams On Toast' on CD, vinyl or cassette here: https://thedarkness.lnk.to/dreamsontoast/
Stream / Download the latest single 'I Hate Myself': https://thedarkness.lnk.to/ihm

The Darkness are also going on tour across the UK in March, tickets are on sale here: https://www.thedarknesslive.com/tour-dates/

For Cameo messages: https://www.cameo.com/justinhawkins

Talk to me on my Patreon:  http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

Get a Justin Hawkins Rides Again T-Shirt & Hoodie here: https://thejawsofvictory

title: Squid: Ignoring Melody (But In A Good Way)
